        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nwould version range (1.1.9999, 1.2.99999) be more beneficial ?\n\nOnce 1.2.0 artifacts are ready, maven may pull it without issue, but can cause issue while working with OSGI. As:\n\nIn Maven:   X.Y.Z-SNAPSHOT < X.Y.Z (released version)\nIn OSGI :   X.Y.Z-SNAPSHOT > X.Y.Z (released version)",
